FME boasts a team of qualified faculty members with diverse research interests. Notable faculty include:

- **Prof. Dr. Wasim Ahmed Khan**: Specializes in Virtual Reality, Virtual Manufacturing, Operations Research, and Education Management. :contentReference[oaicite:0]{index=0}
- **Dr. Khalid Rahman**: Focuses on Electrohydrodynamic Inkjet Printing, Direct Write Technologies, Printed and Flexible Devices, and Wearable Devices. :contentReference[oaicite:1]{index=1}
- **Dr. Massab Junaid**: Researches Metal Joining, Laser and Wire-Arc Metal Deposition, Residual Stresses in Structures, and Thermo-Mechanical Processing.

FMCE comprises two main departments:

- **Department of Materials Science and Engineering (DMSE)**: Offers programs focused on the understanding and application of materials science, preparing students for careers in academia, research, business, and industry. :contentReference[oaicite:1]{index=1}
- **Department of Chemical Engineering (DCHE)**: Provides education and training in chemical engineering, emphasizing innovation, sustainability, and a positive impact on society. :contentReference[oaicite:2]{index=2}

FMCE offers four-year Bachelor of Science (BS) degree programs in:

- **Materials Engineering**: Specializations include Manufacturing and Nanotechnology. :contentReference[oaicite:3]{index=3}
- **Chemical Engineering**: Focuses on designing, process dynamics, synthesizing energy sectors, and materials production. :contentReference[oaicite:4]{index=4}

FMCE boasts a team of qualified faculty members with diverse research interests. Notable faculty include:

- **Prof. Dr. F. Ahmad Khalid, SI**: Rector and Professor with research interests in nanotechnology and materials engineering. :contentReference[oaicite:6]{index=6}
- **Prof. Dr. Fahd Nawaz Khan**: Dean and Professor specializing in machining and joining of high-performance alloys. :contentReference[oaicite:7]{index=7}
- **Dr. Muhammad Imran Khan**: Dean (Student Affairs) and Associate Professor focusing on smart materials for engineering and biomedical applications.

DCE boasts a team of qualified faculty members with diverse research interests. Notable faculty include:

- **Prof. Dr. Muhammad Ashraf Tanoli**: Head of Department, specializing in structural engineering and construction management. :contentReference[oaicite:3]{index=3}
- **Dr. Numan Khan**: Assistant Professor with research interests in AI and machine learning for data analysis, building information modeling, and construction safety monitoring. :contentReference[oaicite:4]{index=4}
- **Dr. Muhammad Waseem**: Assistant Professor focusing on hydrology and water resources engineering. :contentReference[oaicite:5]{index=5}

SMS boasts a team of qualified faculty members with diverse research interests. Notable faculty include:

- **Prof. Dr. Sami Farooq**: Dean and Professor with research interests in Operations and Supply Chain Management. :contentReference[oaicite:4]{index=4}
- **Dr. Yousaf Ali Khan**: Associate Professor specializing in Operations Management and Quantitative Methods. :contentReference[oaicite:5]{index=5}
